src.description: The address of the resource where you want to play the video
src.description_zh: 要播放视频的资源地址

duration.description: Specify the length of the video

controls.description: Whether to display default playback controls (play/pause button, playback progress, time)
controls.description_zh: 是否显示默认播放控件（播放/暂停按钮、播放进度、时间）

danmuBtn.description: Whether or not to display the barrage button is only valid during initialization and cannot be changed dynamically
danmuBtn.description_zh: 是否显示弹幕按钮，只在初始化时有效，不能动态变更

enableDanmu.description: Whether or not to display the barrage is only valid during initialization and cannot be dynamically changed
enableDanmu.description_zh: 是否展示弹幕，只在初始化时有效，不能动态变更

autoplay.description: Whether or not to play automatically

loop.description: Whether or not to play on a loop

initialTime.description: Specify the initial playback position of the video
initialTime.description_zh: 指定视频初始播放位置

pageGesture.description: In non-full-screen mode, whether to enable brightness and volume adjustment gestures
pageGesture.description_zh: 在非全屏模式下，是否开启亮度与音量调节手势

direction.description: Set the orientation of the video when the video is full-screen, and if you don't specify it, it will be automatically determined based on the aspect ratio. Valid values are 0 (normal portrait), 90 (90 degrees counterclockwise), -90 (90 degrees counterclockwise)
direction.description_zh: 设置全屏时视频的方向，不指定则根据宽高比自动判断。有效值为 0（正常竖向）, 90（屏幕逆时针90度）, -90（屏幕顺时针90度）

showProgress.description: If this parameter is not set, it will be displayed only when the width is greater than 240
showProgress.description_zh: 若不设置，宽度大于240时才会显示

showFullscreenBtn.description: Whether to display a full-screen button

showPlayBtn.description: Whether to display the play button in the control bar at the bottom of the video
showPlayBtn.description_zh: 是否显示视频底部控制栏的播放按钮

showCenterPlayBtn.description: Whether to display the play button in the middle of the video
showCenterPlayBtn.description_zh: 是否显示视频中间的播放按钮

enableProgressGesture.description: Whether to turn on gestures to control progress
enableProgressGesture.description_zh: 是否开启控制进度的手势

objectFit.description: The representation of a video when the size of the video is inconsistent with the size of the video container
objectFit.description_zh: 当视频大小与 video 容器大小不一致时，视频的表现形式

poster.description: If the controls property value is false, the poster setting is invalid
poster.description_zh: 视频封面的图片网络资源地址，如果 controls 属性值为 false 则设置 poster 无效

showMuteBtn.description: Whether or not to display a mute button

title.description: The title of the video, which is displayed at the top when it is in full screen
title.description_zh: 视频的标题，全屏时在顶部展示

playBtnPosition.description: The position of the play button - bottom: controls bar - center: in the middle of the video
playBtnPosition.description_zh: 播放按钮的位置- bottom: controls bar 上- center: 视频中间

enablePlayGesture.description: Whether to enable the playback gesture, that is, double-click to switch play/pause
enablePlayGesture.description_zh: 是否开启播放手势，即双击切换播放/暂停

autoPauseIfNavigate.description: When you jump to other Mini Program pages, whether to automatically pause the video on this page
autoPauseIfNavigate.description_zh: 当跳转到其它小程序页面时，是否自动暂停本页面的视频

autoPauseIfOpenNative.description: When you jump to other WeChat native pages, whether to automatically pause the video on this page
autoPauseIfOpenNative.description_zh: 当跳转到其它微信原生页面时，是否自动暂停本页面的视频

vslideGesture.description: In non-full-screen mode, whether to enable brightness and volume adjustment gestures (same as page-gesture)
vslideGesture.description_zh: 在非全屏模式下，是否开启亮度与音量调节手势（同 page-gesture）

vslideGestureInFullscreen.description: In full-screen mode, whether to turn on brightness and volume adjustment gestures
vslideGestureInFullscreen.description_zh: 在全屏模式下，是否开启亮度与音量调节手势

adUnitId.description: The ID of the ad unit in front of the video, for more details, please refer to the open ability video front ad
adUnitId.description_zh: 视频前贴广告单元ID，更多详情可参考开放能力视频前贴广告

posterForCrawler.description: It is recommended to use a video cover image without a playback icon and only support network addresses
posterForCrawler.description_zh: 用于给搜索等场景作为视频封面展示，建议使用无播放 icon 的视频封面图，只支持网络地址

showCastingButton.description: Display the cast button. Only Android and the same layer of rendering takes effect, and supports the DLNA protocol
showCastingButton.description_zh: 显示投屏按钮。只安卓且同层渲染下生效，支持 DLNA 协议

pictureInPictureMode.description: Set the window mode: push, pop, empty string or set multiple modes in array form (e.g. ["push", "pop"])
pictureInPictureMode.description_zh: 设置小窗模式： push, pop，空字符串或通过数组形式设置多种模式（如： ["push", "pop"]）

enableAutoRotation.description: Whether to enable the mobile phone landscape screen will automatically fullscreen, and take effect when the system settings enable automatic rotation
enableAutoRotation.description_zh: 是否开启手机横屏时自动全屏，当系统设置开启自动旋转时生效

showScreenLockButton.description: Whether to display the lock screen button, only when the screen is full, and control the operation of the bar after the lock screen
showScreenLockButton.description_zh: 是否显示锁屏按钮，仅在全屏时显示，锁屏后控制栏的操作

showSnapshotButton.description: Whether or not to display a screenshot button, only when full-screen
showSnapshotButton.description_zh: 是否显示截屏按钮，仅在全屏时显示

showBackgroundPlaybackButton.description: Whether to display the background audio playback button
showBackgroundPlaybackButton.description_zh: 是否展示后台音频播放按钮

backgroundPoster.description: Notification bar icon after entering background audio playback (Android exclusive)
backgroundPoster.description_zh: 进入后台音频播放后的通知栏图标（Android 独有）

nativeProps.description: Used to transparently transfer properties on WebComponents to internal H5 labels
nativeProps.description_zh: 用于透传 WebComponents 上的属性到内部 H5 标签上

showBottomProgress.description: Whether to display the progress bar at the bottom

pictureInPictureShowProgress.description: Whether to display the playback progress in small window mode
pictureInPictureShowProgress.description_zh: 是否在小窗模式下显示播放进度

referrerPolicy.description: The format is fixed to https://servicewechat.com/{appid}/{version}/page-frame.html, where {appid} is the appid of the Mini Program, {version} is the version number of the Mini Program, version number 0 indicates the development version, trial version and audit version, version number is devtools means developer tools, and the rest are official versions;
referrerPolicy.description_zh: 格式固定为 https://servicewechat.com/{appid}/{version}/page-frame.html，其中 {appid} 为小程序的 appid，{version} 为小程序的版本号，版本号为 0 表示为开发版、体验版以及审核版本，版本号为 devtools 表示为开发者工具，其余为正式版本；

isDrm.description: Whether it is a DRM video source or not
isDrm.description_zh: 是否是 DRM 视频源

provisionUrl.description: DRM device authentication URL, only valid when is-drm is true (Android)
provisionUrl.description_zh: DRM 设备身份认证 url，仅 is-drm 为 true 时生效 (Android)

certificateUrl.description: DRM device authentication URL, only when is-drm is true (iOS)
certificateUrl.description_zh: DRM 设备身份认证 url，仅 is-drm 为 true 时生效 (iOS)

licenseUrl.description: DRM obtains the encrypted information URL, which takes effect only when is-drm is true
licenseUrl.description_zh: DRM 获取加密信息 url，仅 is-drm 为 true 时生效

posterSize.description: When the aspect ratio of the poster does not match the height and width of the video, how to display the poster is the same as the background-size.
posterSize.description_zh: 当 poster 高宽比跟视频高宽不匹配时，如何显示 poster，设置规则同 background-size 一致。

showThinProgressBar.description: When the bottom toolbar is hidden, whether to display the thin progress bar (invalid when controls=false).
showThinProgressBar.description_zh: 当底部工具条隐藏时，是否显示细进度条（controls=false 时设置无效）。

mobilenetHintType.description: Mobile network reminder style. 0 - No reminder 1 - tip reminder 2 - Blocking reminder (no traffic consumption) 3 - Blocking reminder (with traffic consumption reminder)
mobilenetHintType.description_zh: 移动网络提醒样式。0 - 不提醒1 - tip 提醒2 - 阻塞提醒(无消耗流量大小)3 - 阻塞提醒(有消耗流量大小提醒)

floatingMode.description: Overlay settings. Global overlays are not supported at this time. Optional value: none: no overlay. page: an in-page overlay.
floatingMode.description_zh: 浮窗设置。暂时不支持全局浮窗。可选值：none：无浮窗。page：页面内浮窗。

showNoWifiTip.description: Whether to display the continued playback overlay in a non-Wi-Fi environment
showNoWifiTip.description_zh: 非 wifi 环境下是否显示继续播放浮层

showLockBtn.description: In full-screen mode, whether to display the lock screen button
showLockBtn.description_zh: 全屏模式下，是否显示锁屏按钮

showRateBtn.description: Whether or not to display a double-speed playback button
showRateBtn.description_zh: 是否显示倍速播放按钮

showVslideBtnInFullscreen.description: In full-screen mode, whether to display the sidebar control buttons
showVslideBtnInFullscreen.description_zh: 全屏模式下，是否显示侧边栏控制按钮

silentPlay.description: Whether to enter the silent video mode, after entering the silent video mode, the video will be played silently and does not respond to the physical volume change of the system
silentPlay.description_zh: 是否进入无声视频模式，进入无声视频模式后，视频将静音播放且不响应系统物理音量变化，点击播放器提示无声视频，手势调节失效

preRollUnitId.description: The unit ID of the pre-roll ad

postRollUnitId.description: The unit ID of the post-posted ad

showPlaybackRateBtn.description: Whether to display the speed control, click the speed control to select the speed control, the optional value: 0.75/1.0/1.25/1.5/2
showPlaybackRateBtn.description_zh: 是否显示倍速控件，点击倍速控件后可选择倍速，可选值： 0.75/1.0/1.25/1.5/2

enablePlayInBackground.description: When the host exits the background during video playback, it opens a small window for playback, which is supported by iOS 14 and later. After exiting the background for the first time, a pop-up window will be given to prompt the user to authorize, and after the authorization is completed, it can be reset in the "Settings" of the Mini Program. For supported scenes, see the background window for playback
enablePlayInBackground.description_zh: video 播放时宿主退出后台后开启小窗播放，iOS 14 及以上版本支持。开启时首次退出后台后给予弹窗提示用户授权，授权完成后可以到小程序「设置」中重设。支持场景见后台小窗播放

preferredPeakBitRate.description: Specify the upper bound of the bitrate, which is measured in bits per second
preferredPeakBitRate.description_zh: 指定码率上界，单位为比特每秒

isLive.description: Whether it is a live source

definition.description: Clarity, sets the definition of the definition list and the default playback. The Toggle Definition button is only displayed when the screen is full, and the description of the properties is detailed in the description of the Definition type. Make sure that one of the src and definition is required, if both src and definition are set, the definition takes precedence over src
definition.description_zh: 清晰度，设置清晰度列表和默认播放的清晰度。切换清晰度按钮仅在全屏时展示，属性说明详见 Definition 类型说明。需要保证 src 和 definition 中有一个为必填，若同时设置了 src 和 definition，definition 优先级高于 src

onPlay.description: The play event is triggered when playback starts/resumes
onPlay.description_zh: 当开始/继续播放时触发 play 事件

onPause.description: The pause event is triggered when playback is paused
onPause.description_zh: 当暂停播放时触发 pause 事件

onEnded.description: The ended event is triggered when the playback reaches the end
onEnded.description_zh: 当播放到末尾时触发 ended 事件

onTimeUpdate.description: Triggered when the playback progress changes, the trigger frequency is 250ms once
onTimeUpdate.description_zh: 播放进度变化时触发, 触发频率 250ms 一次

onFullscreenChange.description: Triggered when the video enters and exits full screen
onFullscreenChange.description_zh: 当视频进入和退出全屏时触发

onError.description: Triggered when there is an error in video playback

onProgress.description: Triggered when the loading progress changes, only one section of loading is supported
onProgress.description_zh: 加载进度变化时触发，只支持一段加载

onLoadedMetaData.description: Triggered when the video metadata is loaded
onLoadedMetaData.description_zh: 视频元数据加载完成时触发

onEnterPictureInPicture.description: The player enters the small window

onSeekComplete.description: Triggered when the seek is completed

onFullScreenChange.description: Triggered when the video enters and exits full screen
onFullScreenChange.description_zh: 视频进入和退出全屏时触发

onControlsToggle.description: Toggles controls to be displayed and hidden.
onControlsToggle.description_zh: 切换 controls 显示隐藏时触发。

onTap.description: Triggered when you click Video view
onTap.description_zh: 点击视频 view 时触发

onRenderStart.description: Triggered when the video actually starts playing after loading.
onRenderStart.description_zh: 当视频加载完真正开始播放时触发。

onAdStart.description: Triggered when an in-roll ad starts playing
onAdStart.description_zh: 贴片广告开始播放时触发

onAdEnded.description: Triggered at the end of the roll
onAdEnded.description_zh: 贴片广告播放结束时触发

onAdClose.description: Triggered at the unnatural end of an in-roll ad, such as when the user closes the ad or the video component is destroyed during ad playback
onAdClose.description_zh: 贴片广告非自然结束时触发，如：用户关闭广告或广告播放过程中 video 组件被销毁

onAdError.description: Triggered when an in-roll ad fails to load
onAdError.description_zh: 贴片广告加载失败时触发

onPlayBackRateChange.description: Triggered when the video speed change is completed. Returns the changed speed value
onPlayBackRateChange.description_zh: 视频倍速改变完成时触发。返回改变后的倍速值

onMuteChange.description: Triggered when the mute state change is complete. Returns whether the current silence is currently silent
onMuteChange.description_zh: 静音状态改变完成时触发。返回当前是否静音

onControlTap.description: Triggered when a control is tapped. Returns the type of control you are currently clicking
onControlTap.description_zh: 点击控件时触发。返回当前点击的控件类型

onEnterBackground.description: Triggered when entering the small window for playback

onCloseBackground.description: Triggered when the widget is closed for playback

onLeaveBackground.description: Triggered when you leave the window and enter the app
onLeaveBackground.description_zh: 离开小窗进入 app 事件时触发

onAdLoad.description: 贴片广告加载成功时触发，event.detail = { adType: 'preRollAd' or 'postRollAd' }
onAdLoad.description_zh: 贴片广告加载成功时触发，event.detail = { adType: 'preRollAd' or 'postRollAd' }

onCastingUserSelect.description: 用户选择投屏设备时触发 detail = { state: "success"/"fail" }
onCastingUserSelect.description_zh: 用户选择投屏设备时触发 detail = { state: "success"/"fail" }

onCastingStateChange.description: 投屏成功/失败时触发 detail = { type, state: "success"/"fail" }
onCastingStateChange.description_zh: 投屏成功/失败时触发 detail = { type, state: "success"/"fail" }

onCastingInterrupt.description: Triggered when the projection is interrupted
